  Traits: 
  Description: Your ancestors have always had a connection to fire and a thicker
    skin, which allows you to resist burning. You gain fire resistance equal to half
    your level minimum 1). You can also recover from being on fire more easily. Your
    flat check to remove persistent fire damage is DC 10 instead of DC 15, which
    is reduced to DC 5 if another creature uses a particularly appropriate action
    to help.
